{
  "description": "Jieli/Free3-P macro pad: Top single-tap -> Fn (Typeless) / double-tap -> Command+V (paste), Middle single-tap -> Shift+Return (newline) / double-tap -> Return (send), Bottom single-tap -> Up arrow / double-tap -> Down arrow. USB uses Karabiner-side tap/double-tap detection (Ctrl+X for both presses); BT mode 4 uses pad-firmware-side detection (equal_sign for single tap, Option+Z for double tap). Matches both USB and Bluetooth transports.",
